    {
      "id": "1ac4750c-f3ba-80f4-971e-cf79ef470526",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors make an interest argument when it comes to recommender systems: its better for the model to not make stupid recommendations. Authors thus, propose what is stupidity and what data-driven techniques may exist to avoid it.",
